flowchart TB
    DEV[Developer Pushes Code to GitHub] --> JEN[Jenkins Pipeline Triggered]

    subgraph PIPE["Jenkins CI/CD Pipeline Stages"]
        direction TB
        S1[1. Checkout Source Code]
        S2[2. Install Dependencies and Run Tests]
